      "comment": "GOOSEBUMPS RICO (6) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Billy Ray Mikado (24.45) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Goes very well from this draw with three wins and three minor placings from six starts. Can measure up this time. ENERGISER DASH (8) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (22.59) last time in a Grade 5 at Ballarat. Worth following up. COLLINDA POPS (7) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at Warragul in a handy 23.13 beating Rose Opal. Expected to feature again. PAW UCARTY (4) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
